# Title: Add New Download Source To Winget
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-04-17
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects usage of winget to add new additional download sources
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1059
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_winget_add_custom_source.yml
# False Positives:
#   - False positive are expected with legitimate sources

CommandLine="*source *" CommandLine="*add *" Image="*\\winget.exe" OR OriginalFileName="winget.exe"